doc.ContractDescription: IGF::OT::IGF CONTRACTOR STATEMENT OF RELEASE IN CONSIDERATION OF THE MODIFICATION(S) AGREED TO HEREIN AS COMPLETE EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENTS FOR THE CONTRACTORS REVISED PROPOSAL 06/28/2016 FOR THE JUDGE MUNLEY CHAMBERS PAINTING AND WALLPAPER, THE CONTRACTOR HEREBY RELEASES THE GOVERNMENT FROM ANY AND ALL LIABILITY UNDER THIS CONTRACT FOR FURTHER EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENTS ATTRIBUTABLE TO SUCH FACTS OR CIRCUMSTANCES GIVING RISE TO THE PROPOSAL(S) FOR ADJUSTMENT MODIFICATION PS01. THIS MODIFICATION INCREASES THE AMOUNT BY $1,840.65 FROM $17,125.92 TO MAKE THE TOTAL OF THE ENTIRE CONTRACT $18,966.57. THE INCREASE IS TO PAINT EXISTING FLOORS, CEILING, WALLS, OR PARTITIONS. THIS IS A CHANGE ORDER MODIFICATION OF THE PROJECT DESCRIBED PER THE ATTACHED SCOPE OF WORK, ORDER NUMBER GS-P-03-16-QK-7130. ALL OTHER TERMS AND CONDITIONS WILL REMAIN THE SAME. THE CONTRACT COMPLETION DATE IS EXTENDED FROM SEPTEMBER 30, 2016 TO OCTOBER 31, 2016. IT IS AGREED THAT THE EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENT PROVIDED FOR IN THIS MODIFICATION CONSTITUTES AN ACCORD AND SATISFACTION OF ANY AND ALL PAST, PRESENT AND FUTURE CLAIMS FOR ADDITIONAL MONETARY COMPENSATION AND TIME FOR THE ACCOMPLISHMENT OF THE WORK DESCRIBED IN THIS MODIFICATION.
